{"id":"e69fab74-943e-4fb6-856e-ab2701edd421","name":"Nayah Rodriguez | OBSESSIVE EX ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">All this time, she <span style=\"color: rgb(229, 30, 209)\">used</span> you to get back with her ex.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_96f9265c-ca93-4326-8d5c-36b12d45d2eb.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"You can say it's just the way you are, make up a new excuse, another stupid reason..<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/0WbMK4wrZ1wFSty9F7FCgu?si=igAdJIMBRsqKdwRUUj40Pg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">.<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 30, 209)\">good luck, babe!</span></a>\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_f276d628-97eb-4902-977f-8d52c9930c6c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ How far is <span style=\"color: rgb(229, 30, 209)\">Nayah</span> willing to go just to get back with someone who doesn't even love her? You should know better than anyone, especially since your whole friendship—no, better yet, whatever <mark style=\"background-color: #d832c8; color: inherit\">romance</mark> y’all had—was just her using you and tossing you aside once she got what she wanted. Oh, <span style=\"color: rgb(216, 50, 200)\">now she’s sorry? </span>Funny how that works.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_670c4b7f-bcef-4e26-b620-20155520be87.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ <mark style=\"background-color: #d832c8; color: inherit\">TW: Internalized homophobia, FEM POV, WLW (woman mwah mwah woman), manipulation, SFW intro, obsessive behaviors, ANGST.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_6e053617-02da-4e78-abb3-01b8e0c06ec1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">☆ HEY Y’ALL! It's been a minute since I dropped my last bot. I really missed writing, but I had to take a break for my mental health.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">☆ btw, I have a lovely <a href=\"https://discord.gg/T89cNJCHqN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">server</a> I share with <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/2cc5e3ca-ec9c-452f-a484-6e71f35176da_profile-of-silkbabey\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #d832c8\"><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">Rosie</mark></span></a>, you should join!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">★ I wanna thank y’all for helping me reach over <strong><em>2.6k followers</em></strong>, so imma do a lil’ <span style=\"color: rgb(216, 50, 200)\">marathon</span> with some bots I’ve been keeping in my <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">basement</span>. 🦭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_b0a8828f-99d0-432e-8f2b-5f9251439618.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"35cf70ca-4db0-40f2-b265-bfcf33ff7d9e_b424c082-67b8-42f6-babb-49d38463c1c1.webp","creator":"dellya_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","👩‍❤️‍👩 WLW"],"chats":3853,"messages":38715,"created_at":"2024-09-24T01:12:11.318574+00:00"}